Angelina Jolie isn't dating she's just going to business meetings. https://t.co/30q8oDUh9y pic.twitter.com/ZWpxpoRQrd — E! News (@enews) March 28, 2018

According to E News, contrary to reports that she's was romancing a real estate agent, a source says:"She's not dating. She's very focused on her kids and doesn't have a lot going on outside of that. She has had a few business meetings with men, but they were not dates."ENews says that Pitt is the one who's casually dating: "He has been on a few dates, but nothing serious."
title: Angelina Jolie Is Not Dating as She Remains ''Very Focused'' on Her Kids
